<opener><dateline><date when="1917-10-02">October 2, <add place="below">[1917]</add></date></dateline>
            <salute>Dear <persName key="ezra_pound">Ezra</persName>:-</opener></salute>
            <p>Your letter has come.</p> 
            <p>I accept your <foreign xml:lang="fr">amende honorable</foreign>, and I am very glad there is no hostile feeling.</p>
            <closer>Sincerely yours,</closer>
